org.locationtech.geowave.core.store.query.filter

Interface QueryFilter

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Persistable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AdapterIdQueryFilter, BasicQueryFilter, CoordinateRangeQueryFilter, CQLQueryFilter, CustomQueryConstraintsWithFilter.InternalCustomQueryFilter, DataIdQueryFilter, DataIdRangeQueryFilter, DedupeFilter, DistortionGroupManagement.BatchIdFilter, FilterList, InsertionIdQueryFilter, PrefixIdQueryFilter, SpatialQueryFilter

    public interface QueryFilter
extends Persistable
    A simple filter interface to determine inclusion/exclusion based on a generic persistence encoding. Client-side filters will be given an AdapterPersistenceEncoding but distributable filters will be given a generic PersistenceEncoding.
